{"title":"位运算实现加减乘除","slug":"位运算实现加减乘除","date":"2021-03-16T12:06:34.000Z","updated":"2021-03-31T08:34:52.261Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/位运算实现加减乘除.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"通过位运算模拟底层的加减乘除操作，理解计算机最底层的实现方式。","covers":null,"content":"<p>通过位运算模拟底层的加减乘除操作，理解计算机最底层的实现方式。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>加法：</p>\n<p>学习过数字电路的都知道加法器是通过异或，与，或等逻辑操作实现的。通过半加器实现全加器。半加器公式如下</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\ns=a\\oplus b</script><script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\nc_{out}=a \\& b</script><p>通过迭代半加器，直到</p>\n<script type=\"math/tex; mode=display\">\nc_{out}==0</script><p>此时的s即是最终结果，即可实现全加器。</p>\n<p>减法：</p>\n<p>利用补码机制转换成加法实现。</p>\n<p>乘法：</p>\n<p>传统乘法器和布斯乘法器实现。布斯乘法器的原理可参考<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/127164011。\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/127164011。</a></p>\n<p>除法：</p>\n<p>目前还没有想到比较好的底层实现方式，（凑数）。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span 